   "source": [
    "## Step 7. Create a proof of concept\n",
    "\n",
    "Create a proof-of-concept to verify your project idea will work.\n",
    "You can (and probably should) do this before you spend a lot of time cleaning your data in the previous step.\n",
    "The goal of the proof of concept is to make sure that you can get at least close to your ideal outputs given your inputs.\n",
    "\n",
    "> I spent as little time as possible feeding the rule book into an off-the-shelf question-answering system\n",
    "> to see if the answers (outputs) to various questions (inputs) were at least close to what I wanted.\n",
    ">\n",
    "> I did this just using a simple notebook."
   ]
